Installation Instructions
=========================

Unix:
-----

    ensure that vim-5.5 or better is installed

    cp macros/bracketing.base.vim ~/.vim.bracketing.base

    cp macros/bracketing.meta.vim ~/.vim.bracketing
    or
    cp macros/bracketing.no-meta.vim ~/.vim.bracketing

    edit .vim.bracketing and change the "source" line to
	source ~/.vim.bracketing.base

    edit your .vimrc and add the line:
	source ~/.vim.bracketing

Windows:
--------

    ensure that vim-5.5 or better is installed
	set the environment variable "VIM" to the directory where vim
	was installed
	set the environment variable "HOME" to something useful: ie:
	    c:\my_stuff

    copy macros/bracketing.base.vim to _vim.bracketing.base in your
	HOME directory

    copy macros/bracketing.meta.vim to _vim.bracketing
    or
    copy macros/bracketing.no-meta.vim _vim.bracketing
    in your HOME directory

    edit _vim.bracketing and change the "source" line to

	source c:\my_stuff\_vim.bracketing.base

    (ie: the full path to the _vim.bracketing.base file)

    edit your .vimrc and add the line:

	source c:\my_stuff\_vim.bracketing

    (ie: the full path to the _vim.bracketing file)
